metadata.name: The Factory Resurrected #1/12
metadata.description: Step into the vibrant world of Andy Warhol, where old meets new in a stunning display of artistry. Our unique blend of artificial intelligence and ultra-photographic techniques has brought his iconic works to life, imbued with the boldness and energy that made Warhol a cultural icon.  Join us on a journey of creativity and innovation as we celebrate the legendary legacy of Andy Warhol.
